dc_title_s: Map of the Ohio portion of East Fork of Whitewater River Basin and the Twin Creek Basin showing availability of underground water
dc_description_s: Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water|Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.|Scale bar lower right corner of map.|Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Whitewater River (east fork) and Twin Creek Basins and quality of underground water.
